<main class="page-grid">
  <section class="content-area prose-panel">
    <nav class="breadcrumbs"><%= link_to "ホーム", root_path %><span>›</span><span>プロフィール</span></nav>
    <h1>プロフィール</h1>
    <div class="profile-page-card">
      <% if current_site_setting.profile_image.attached? %>
        <%= image_tag current_site_setting.profile_image, alt: current_site_setting.profile_name, class: "avatar-image" %>
      <% else %>
        <div class="avatar-drawing" aria-hidden="true"><span class="face"></span></div>
      <% end %>
      <div>
        <h2><%= current_site_setting.profile_name %></h2>
        <p class="role"><%= current_site_setting.profile_title %></p>
        <% if current_site_setting.profile_email.present? %>
          <p><%= mail_to current_site_setting.profile_email %></p>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p><%= current_site_setting.profile_bio %></p>
    <p>AWS、IaC、自動化、SRE、Observabilityを中心に、日々の業務と個人実験で学んだことを記録しています。</p>
    <% if current_site_setting.sns_visible? %>
      <div class="social-icons profile-links">
        <%= social_link "GitHub", current_site_setting.github_url, aria: { label: "GitHub" } %>
        <%= social_link "X", current_site_setting.x_url, aria: { label: "X" } %>
        <%= link_to "RSS", current_site_setting.rss_url.presence || feed_path(format: :xml), aria: { label: "RSS" } %>
        <%= social_link "Zenn", current_site_setting.zenn_url, aria: { label: "Zenn" } %>
        <%= social_link "note", current_site_setting.note_url, aria: { label: "note" } %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </section>
  <%= render "shared/sidebar", categories: @categories, archives: @archives %>
</main>
